  "detailed_description": "<h1>VFC Online Community Invitation</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/extras/135ae4073df543fcdad71a298ddcb9cc.poster.avif?t=1732315593\" width=580 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/extras/135ae4073df543fcdad71a298ddcb9cc.webm?t=1732315593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/extras/135ae4073df543fcdad71a298ddcb9cc.mp4?t=1732315593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>VFC Online Community hosts weekly casual fights and seasonal tournaments, where everyone can register to participate!<br><br>Register your interest at our discord!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Offical VFC Discord:</h2></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ATTENTION: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Virtual Fighting Championship (VFC)</strong> brings the heart-pounding action of classic fighting games like <i>Street Fighter</i> and <i>Tekken</i> into an immersive VR world. With a perfect balance of realism and over-the-top excitement, VFC delivers a combat experience that rewards real-life skills while making every fight dynamic and engaging.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/extras/8b7fe833925620aba799a9957f868bdc.poster.avif?t=1732315593\" width=570 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/extras/8b7fe833925620aba799a9957f868bdc.webm?t=1732315593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/extras/8b7fe833925620aba799a9957f868bdc.mp4?t=1732315593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're taking on players from around the world in online matches or perfecting your techniques against a lineup of unique NPC opponents, VFC puts you in control of the action. Each fight is a dynamic, fast-paced showdown where strategy and creativity lead to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy to pick up but endlessly rewarding to master, VFC offers gameplay for everyone—from casual players looking for fun to competitive fighters aiming for the top. Step into the arena, choose your style, and fight your way in this exciting and highly replayable VR fighting experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/extras/c729e8be93e4a5168cb6c59fcf7b41da.poster.avif?t=1732315593\" width=580 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/extras/c729e8be93e4a5168cb6c59fcf7b41da.webm?t=1732315593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/extras/c729e8be93e4a5168cb6c59fcf7b41da.mp4?t=1732315593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ATTENTION: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Virtual Fighting Championship (VFC)</strong> brings the heart-pounding action of classic fighting games like <i>Street Fighter</i> and <i>Tekken</i> into an immersive VR world. With a perfect balance of realism and over-the-top excitement, VFC delivers a combat experience that rewards real-life skills while making every fight dynamic and engaging.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/extras/8b7fe833925620aba799a9957f868bdc.poster.avif?t=1732315593\" width=570 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/extras/8b7fe833925620aba799a9957f868bdc.webm?t=1732315593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/extras/8b7fe833925620aba799a9957f868bdc.mp4?t=1732315593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're taking on players from around the world in online matches or perfecting your techniques against a lineup of unique NPC opponents, VFC puts you in control of the action. Each fight is a dynamic, fast-paced showdown where strategy and creativity lead to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy to pick up but endlessly rewarding to master, VFC offers gameplay for everyone—from casual players looking for fun to competitive fighters aiming for the top. Step into the arena, choose your style, and fight your way in this exciting and highly replayable VR fighting experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/extras/c729e8be93e4a5168cb6c59fcf7b41da.poster.avif?t=1732315593\" width=580 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/extras/c729e8be93e4a5168cb6c59fcf7b41da.webm?t=1732315593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779130/extras/c729e8be93e4a5168cb6c59fcf7b41da.mp4?t=1732315593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
